@startuml

title Nordility Repository Architecture (Contributor Blueprint)
left to right direction
!pragma layout elk

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam ArrowColor #2F4F4F
skinparam ArrowThickness 2
skinparam ArrowFontSize 12
skinparam titleFontSize 26
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam packageFontSize 18
skinparam packageFontStyle bold
skinparam rectangleFontSize 12
skinparam rectangleFontName Arial
skinparam DefaultTextAlignment left
skinparam LegendFontSize 14

package "Entry Surface" as ENTRY_PANEL #F5F5F5 {
  rectangle "CLI\nsrc/nordility/cli.py\n- argparse verbs: connect/disconnect/change/watch-wireguard/web/list-groups\n- logging setup\n- stdout/stderr + exit codes" as CLI #DAE8FC
  rectangle "Module Entry\nsrc/nordility/__main__.py\n- python -m nordility" as MOD #DAE8FC
  rectangle "Public Package Surface\nsrc/nordility/__init__.py\n- re-exports NordVPNClient\n- compatibility helpers" as API #DAE8FC
}

package "Configuration + Core Client" as CORE_PANEL #F5F5F5 {
  rectangle "Configuration Resolution\nresolve_executable()\n- explicit arg\n- NORDILITY_EXECUTABLE\n- NORDVPN_EXECUTABLE\n- default Windows path\n\nresolve_backend()\n- auto / windows / cli\n- NORDILITY_BACKEND override" as CONFIG #D5E8D4

  rectangle "NordVPNClient\n- connect / disconnect / change\n- list_groups / pick_group\n- build command tuples\n- dispatch to backend\n- inject launcher / runner / sleeper / rng" as CLIENT #D5E8D4

  rectangle "WireGuard Watcher\nwatch_nordvpn_wireguard()\n- poll nordvpn status + nordlynx state\n- detect route/fwmark drift\n- repair user-managed WireGuard only" as WATCH #D5E8D4
  rectangle "WireGuard Watcher\nwatch_nordvpn_wireguard()\n- poll nordvpn status + nordlynx state\n- start configured wg0 if down\n- repair user-managed WireGuard only" as WATCH #D5E8D4

  rectangle "Web Control\nsrc/nordility/web.py\n- localhost HTTP server\n- Safari/Caddy actions\n- power / rotate / group select" as WEB #D5E8D4

  rectangle "Group Pools\nFAST_GROUPS / FULL_GROUPS\n- underscore-separated names\n- fast/full selection" as GROUPS #D5E8D4

  rectangle "Result + Errors\nCommandResult\nConfigurationError\nCommandExecutionError\nNordilityError" as RESULT #D5E8D4
}

package "Execution Backends" as BACKEND_PANEL #F5F5F5 {
  rectangle "Windows Backend\n- subprocess.Popen\n- NordVPN.exe flags: -c / -d / -g\n- preserves group underscores\n- optional post-launch sleep" as WIN #FFE6CC

  rectangle "CLI Backend\n- subprocess.run\n- nordvpn connect/disconnect\n- converts underscores to spaces\n- captures stdout/stderr/return code" as CLIBACK #FFE6CC
}

package "Testing" as TEST_PANEL #F5F5F5 {
  rectangle "tests/test_client.py\n- unittest\n- backend resolution\n- command construction\n- fake launcher/runner/sleeper\n- deterministic RNG injection" as TESTS #FFF2CC
}

MOD --> CLI
CLI --> CLIENT : parsed subcommands
CLI --> WATCH : watch-wireguard
CLI --> WEB : web
API --> CLIENT : wrapper calls
CONFIG --> CLIENT : executable + backend
CONFIG --> WATCH : executable + backend
CONFIG --> WEB : executable + backend
GROUPS --> CLIENT : fast/full pools
GROUPS --> WEB : group select
CLIENT --> WIN : backend=windows
CLIENT --> CLIBACK : backend=cli
WATCH --> CLIBACK : backend=cli
WEB --> CLIBACK : backend=cli
WIN --> RESULT : launch result or error
CLIBACK --> RESULT : completed process or error
RESULT --> CLI : print message / exit status
TESTS ..> CLIENT : inject fakes
TESTS ..> WATCH
TESTS ..> WEB
TESTS ..> CONFIG
TESTS ..> GROUPS

legend right
  == Primary Flows ==
  CLI: argparse -> NordVPNClient -> backend command -> message/exit code
  Watcher: argparse/systemd -> watch-wireguard -> WireGuard route repair
  Web: Safari/Caddy -> localhost web -> NordVPNClient -> WireGuard repair
  Python API: helper -> NordVPNClient -> CommandResult or legacy status string

  == Key Commands ==
  - PYTHONPATH=src python -m nordility --help
  - PYTHONPATH=src python -m unittest discover -s tests
endlegend

@enduml
